#: Game.Levels.Welcome.L01_Welcome
msgid "# Welcome to Finite Mathematics!\n"
"\n"
"In this course you will learn about the finite-object infrastructure that\n"
"underlies much of formalized mathematics: §0, §1, §2, §3,\n"
"big operators, and the counting identities that power combinatorics and algebra.\n"
"\n"
"**What you need**: familiarity with Lean 4 at the level of the Natural Number\n"
"Game. You should be comfortable with §4, §5, §6, §7, §8,\n"
"and §9.\n"
"\n"
"Let's start with something simple to make sure everything works.\n"
"The §10 tactic can automatically verify decidable propositions — including\n"
"concrete statements about natural numbers and finite types.\n"
"\n"
"Try closing this goal:"
msgstr ""
